name: Delcatty
author: Kagemaru Himeno
flavor_text: It is highly popular among female Trainers for its sublime fur. It does not keep a nest.

poke_body.name: Attracting Body
poke_body.effect: If Delcatty is your Active Pokémon and is damaged by an opponent’s attack (even if Delcatty is Knocked Out), flip a coin. If heads, the Attacking Pokémon is now Confused.

attacks.name: Energy Assist
attacks.effect: Search your discard pile for a basic Energy card and attach it to 1 of your Benched Pokémon.
